---
title: Classic Roasted Chicken Thigh Sheet Pan with Potatoes, Green Beans and Cream of Chicken Gravy
description: The classic meat-and-potatoes is revamped in this tasty dinner. Roasted creamy potatoes and sweet red onions share the same baking sheet as juicy roasted chicken thighs for a super simple clean-up. Tender green beans and a creamy chicken sauce finish the meal off!
